name: tired pixels #4
description: This area of ​​the city could be recognized with closed eyes by the sweet and sour aromas from the counters with oriental food. What was not here: real black soil, hair follicle sprays, cyber-modified rats, metauniverses for dreams, machines for extracting egregors, reference books of retrograde Sirius, translucent cream clothes, liquid crystal puzzles, neural network prostheses, a huge number of books on antibranding, random  cereal with flavor settings, rare newspaper samples of the latest iPhones, simulators of the Tibetan Book of Death, freelance flowers, perfumery with industrial fragrances…
